casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Braylock et al., Appellees.

[Cite as State v. Braylock (1992), 65 Ohio St.3d 11.]

(No. 91-1518 — Submitted July 29, 1992 — Decided October 7, 1992.) Anthony G. Pizza, Prosecuting Attorney, and Mary Sue Barone, for appellant. Scott E. Spencer, for appellees.

The cause is reversed on authority of State v. Gill (1992), 63 Ohio St.3d 53, 584 N.E.2d 1200.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
